Para conectarse

	./lncli --lnddir=/tmp/lnd --network=testnet connect 03a13a469bae4785e27fae24e7664e648cfdb976b97f95c694dea5e55e7d302846@lightning-test.puzzle.ch:9735

Para abrir un canal

	./lncli --lnddir=/tmp/lnd --network=testnet openchannel 03a13a469bae4785e27fae24e7664e648cfdb976b97f95c694dea5e55e7d302846 20000

